{"tid":813893,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇試過俾好姊妹/兄弟搶男/女朋友","createTime":"2018-09-10T22:28:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T11:33:02.000Z","uid":199926,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"85ba18a84f0dfcfd92366fd0c31afd039e0abb3b","tid":813893,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T22:28:33.000Z","msg":"試過俾咗exex個電話個好姊妹知<br />\n之後佢哋就開始傾閒計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個就來者不拒 明知係好姊妹個男朋友都當佢係普通朋友照樣傾閒計 唔識避忌<br />\n個exex表面上/一開頭講關於我嘅野 實質上係想搵佢傾計 最尾分手仲話返我唔應該控制佢 同咩人傾計係佢嘅自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但諗諗下其實佢地兩個本身都好有問題 物以類聚姐 <br />\n<br />\n到下一個ex我都諗左好耐應唔應該俾佢電話又係呢個好姊妹知 點知俾咗又係中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過同ex鬧交跟住佢就去搵我個好姊妹傾訴 <br />\n傾傾吓就變咗佢係我好姊妹面前數我不是<br />\n我問ex佢就話想問佢點氹番我姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講真 兩個人嘅事應該兩個人之間解決<br />\n要牽涉第三者段關係已經有問題<br />\n<br />\n所以如果男朋友同好姊妹/女朋友同好兄弟撻得著<br />\n證明佢地兩個本身都有問題/你同佢地價值觀唔同 早甩早著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad1d2c9f23d8af06d95636eed230c7afb641a6a7","tid":813893,"uid":143468,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T22:36:23.000Z","msg":"搶得走已經代表唔重要 所以冇去阻止 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"154648804c5a51a75a04891e21f75267139675c6","tid":813893,"uid":199926,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T22:47:26.000Z","msg":"重點黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到左現任佢又碰上呢個好姊妹 但現任不單止眼尾都唔會稍下佢 連佢ig direct(問關於我既野)現任 現仼都唔會覆<br />\n好姊妹仲會怪現仼點解咁cool對女朋友既好姊妹咁無禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係要多謝呢個好姊妹幫我每次幫我測試男朋友睇清班賤男<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵到現仼呢個好男人之後我都同好姊妹絕交左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4527b0d3e402d780ae6a116b3680fd93105a750","tid":813893,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad1d2c9f23d8af06d95636eed230c7afb641a6a7","tid":813893,"uid":143468,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T22:36:23.000Z","msg":"搶得走已經代表唔重要 所以冇去阻止 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T22:48:44.000Z","msg":"態度正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c59296054c836544c5471572110feb405bf554","tid":813893,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4527b0d3e402d780ae6a116b3680fd93105a750","tid":813893,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad1d2c9f23d8af06d95636eed230c7afb641a6a7","tid":813893,"uid":143468,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T22:36:23.000Z","msg":"搶得走已經代表唔重要 所以冇去阻止 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T22:48:44.000Z","msg":"態度正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T22:49:18.000Z","msg":"*<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c1b3fe7485f6e0fe1a14762b3d6e8d300d9bf16","tid":813893,"uid":134002,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T22:56:19.000Z","msg":"點解搶完一次exex仲可以繼續做好姊妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2dc181a2c669b5cfc85586795066fa55261ef7","tid":813893,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2c1b3fe7485f6e0fe1a14762b3d6e8d300d9bf16","tid":813893,"uid":134002,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T22:56:19.000Z","msg":"點解搶完一次exex仲可以繼續做好姊妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T23:01:16.000Z","msg":"咁佢又真係無搶到手 淨係不停傾計囉 不過成件事好複雜要講有排講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s